messages.text: I lost my phone last night
yes. it was in a puddle
i mean I guess it works
but you can see the screen and everything?
oh okay where can I meet you?
I get off work at 7 at stellas
oh great that’s right near where I live
cool yea I’ll just have it with me
Hey outside Stellas, are you around?
Ha I guess I should have asked what you look like
Sitting by the bar, next to the weird portrait
Hey just wanted to see if you’re here, getting late
Listen I don’t appreciate you wasting my time
Look I really need my phone
that’s a serious breach of privacy man
i was looking to see what u looked like
to recognize u at the bar
i’ll give you $500 to leave it by the side of the road on embarcadero
just leave it in an envelope we don’t even have to meet
look i don’t want any trouble
but i think its worth more than that
or else im gonna go to the police
I think they’d be really interested in your pics
but if you knew the story you’d understand
bc im not sure why im wasting my time talking to someone who could do that to a woman
i got the names of everyone who works the bar at stellas
you’re one of five people and i can find where you live
you should look at her again
i need to know you haven’t called the cops
what color drapes do you have
You think you can threaten me
you really should move to an interior room
listen i’ll give you the stupid phone
i’ll put it through the mail slot
i’ll even smash it for you if you want
but i need you to promise me something
promise you haven’t sent the picture anywhere
i think that’s a chance i can’t take
